{"tid":898904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀整型美容診所昏迷女子早上不治","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T05:49:32.000Z","uid":167451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"115590d80253685b8e2ee4e2de621c46d8812763","tid":898904,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名女子昨日在尖沙咀一間美容中心接受醫學美容療程後昏迷，延至今早不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方及衞生署派員到位於尖沙咀格蘭中心的一間美容中心調查後離開。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的52歲女病人昨晚在診所內昏迷，被送到伊利沙伯醫院，延至今早九時許不治，涉事的美容診所負責人是西醫李宏邦。消息指他被查問時，最初聲稱為病人治療哮喘，其後承認曾為她注射肉毒桿菌。<br />\n<br />\n現年86歲的李宏邦是外科醫生，他03年為一名女病人抽脂，但病人及後死亡，他於09年被醫委會裁定專業失德，被罰停牌5個月。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E6%95%B4%E5%9E%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB-023903211.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2592%2580%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB-023903211.html&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu910Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=903dcb24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80%E6%95%B4%E5%9E%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB-023903211.html</a>"},{"pid":"28617f80fc4f876bc6b3b8f9aa8012d46e9aae85","tid":898904,"uid":167451,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>他03年為一名女病人抽脂，但病人及後死亡，他於09年被醫委會裁定專業失德，被罰停牌5個月。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4060c750e1fc9ef8ffb3eae34c4704374e81f19","tid":898904,"uid":121473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"sco